text: Rosa Bianca Salazar (born July 16, 1985) is an American actress. She is known for the NBC series Parenthood, and the FX anthology series American Horror Story: Murder House. Salazar has appeared in the movies The Divergent Series: Insurgent as Lynn, and Maze Runner: The Scorch Trials and Maze Runner: The Death Cure, as Brenda. She stars in the upcoming movie Alita: Battle Angel (2018) as Alita alongside Christoph Waltz. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1985 births Category:Living people Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors Category:American voice actors Category:Actors from Washington, D.C.
